124
00:16:09,469 --> 00:16:11,261
天哪
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Jesus Christ.{\r}

125
00:16:12,222 --> 00:16:14,014
如果我不是？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}And what if I don't?{\r}

126
00:16:14,308 --> 00:16:15,718
我不能呢？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}What if I can't?{\r}

127
00:16:15,934 --> 00:16:17,594
普通的食物都可能会致命
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Normal food could be lethal.{\r}

128
00:16:17,811 --> 00:16:20,812
如果你没预见到你的那些渴望 你是会去攻击人类的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}If you don't anticipate your cravings, you will attack humans.{\r}

129
00:16:21,023 --> 00:16:24,142
相信我，你潜意识里是不想那么干的
