130
00:16:24,985 --> 00:16:26,776
麦克，你已经无路可退了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}There really is no going back, Michael.{\r}

131
00:16:29,364 --> 00:16:31,072
抱歉
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm sorry.{\r}

132
00:16:31,533 --> 00:16:33,692
听着，我明白你所做的一切
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Look, I understand what you did.{\r}

133
00:16:33,911 --> 00:16:35,654
我很感激
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm grateful.{\r}

134
00:16:36,747 --> 00:16:38,823
你救了我一命
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You saved my life.{\r}

135
00:16:39,458 --> 00:16:40,703
我还没准备好一死
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I wasn't ready to die.{\r}

136
00:16:45,297 --> 00:16:47,290
我不知道
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't know.{\r}

137
00:16:47,508 --> 00:16:48,622
一切都变了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Everything's changed.{\r}

138
00:16:48,967 --> 00:16:51,541
我或许需要些时间 去适应这一切
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I probably need a minute to make it all fit in my head.{\r}

139
00:16:51,762 --> 00:16:53,838
实在太突然了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It's a lot to process all at once.{\r}

140
00:16:55,849 --> 00:16:58,720
听着，去吧 我会在这的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Look, go. I'll be here.{\r}

141
00:16:59,311 --> 00:17:01,802
你只要保证自己能安全的回来
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You just make sure you come back.{\r}

142
00:18:27,065 --> 00:18:28,310
长官
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Sir.{\r}

143
00:18:28,525 --> 00:18:30,933
那些无辜目击者...
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The innocent who witnessed...{\r}

144
00:18:31,153 --> 00:18:32,433
...他们会保持沉默么？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...they've been silenced?{\r}

145
00:18:32,905 --> 00:18:35,193
他们毫发无损, 按照您的命令做的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}But otherwise unharmed, as ordered.{\r}

146
00:18:39,453 --> 00:18:41,991
- 给我看你的情报 - 是，长官
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}- Show me what you have. - Yes, sir.{\r}

147
00:18:47,294 --> 00:18:48,919
两个恶灵武士被杀
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Two Death Dealers were killed.{\r}

148
00:18:49,129 --> 00:18:50,956
我们没发现狼人的尸体
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}We found no Lycan bodies.{\r}

149
