{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...some sort of UV round.{\r}

151
00:18:56,929 --> 00:18:58,008
艾米利亚呢？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Amelia?{\r}

152
00:19:00,807 --> 00:19:02,006
没有生还者
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}No one survived.{\r}

153
00:19:02,226 --> 00:19:04,598
看来克莱文的手下有可能在场...
