155
00:19:07,940 --> 00:19:09,648
维克多呢？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}And Viktor?{\r}

156
00:19:29,962 --> 00:19:33,165
残局里没有玛可斯的痕迹么？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}And no trace of Marcus amongst the ashes?{\r}

157
00:19:33,382 --> 00:19:36,087
他好像把自己的老巢给烧了，长官
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It seems he destroyed his own coven, sir.{\r}

158
00:19:37,344 --> 00:19:39,467
那才不是他的老巢呢
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It was never his coven.{\r}

159
00:20:04,288 --> 00:20:05,616
我们得走了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}We need to go.{\r}

160
00:20:49,166 --> 00:20:51,205
让我独自呆会儿
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Give me a moment.{\r}

161
00:23:09,556 --> 00:23:11,465
找到你了！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}There you are.{\r}

162
00:24:13,787 --> 00:24:15,329
你好！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}How you doing?{\r}

163
00:24:36,685 --> 00:24:38,263
谢谢
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Thank you.{\r}

164
00:25:01,939 --> 00:25:04,807
（俄语）
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}{\r}

165
00:25:46,620 --> 00:25:47,589
电视屏幕：麦克・柯文
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}{\r}

166
00:25:51,239 --> 00:25:52,229
（俄语）
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}{\r}

167
00:26:00,269 --> 00:26:02,676
滚开
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You've got to get away from me.{\r}

168
00:26:04,147 --> 00:26:05,523
滚开！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get away from me!{\r}

169
00:26:05,659 --> 00:26:07,401
（俄语）
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}{\r}

170
00:26:17,744 --> 00:26:19,025
喂？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Hello?{\r}

171
00:26:25,377 --> 00:26:26,705
那儿
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}There.{\r}

172
00:26:29,006 --> 00:26:30,204
麦克・柯文
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Michael Corvin.{\r}

173
00:26:30,424 --> 00:26:31,704
马上调派人手过去
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get the men up there. Now.{\r}

174
00:26:42,477 --> 00:26:44,221
他妈的给我滚开
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get the fuck away from me.{\r}

175
00:27:10,547 --> 00:27:11,745
站住，站住！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Stop. Stop.{\r}

176
00:27:17,513 --> 00:27:18,758
妈的！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Shit.{\r}

177
00:28:44,766 --> 00:28:47,720
麦克，哦，妈的！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Michael. Oh, shit.{\r}

178
00:28:54,735 --> 00:28:57,404
- 来，喝我的血 - 不
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}- Here. Take it. - No.{\r}

179
00:28:57,613 --> 00:28:59,652
麦克，你会死的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Michael, you'll die.{\r}

180
00:29:25,265 --> 00:29:27,009
妈的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Shit.{\r}

181
00:29:27,309 --> 00:29:29,052
你能动么？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Can you move?{\r}

182
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,685
我们必须躲起来
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}We need to go.{\r}

183
00:29:55,671 --> 00:29:56,869
玛可斯
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Marcus.{\r}

184
00:29:57,089 --> 00:29:59,544
我知道你做了些什么，塞琳娜
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I know what you've done, Selene.{\r}

185
