维克多该死，克莱文也是一样
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Viktor deserved his fate and Kraven was no better.{\r}

186
00:30:02,886 --> 00:30:08,011
克莱文已经得到了应有的下场
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Kraven has already reaped the rewards of his own misdeeds.{\r}

187
00:30:08,600 --> 00:30:10,011
至于维克多...
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}And Viktor...{\r}

188
00:30:10,435 --> 00:30:12,891
维克多死几十次...
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Viktor deserved his fate...{\r}

189
00:30:13,105 --> 00:30:14,480
...也是活该
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...many times over.{\r}

190
00:30:16,149 --> 00:30:18,107
他对你家族的大屠杀...
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}A terrible business...{\r}

191
00:30:18,318 --> 00:30:20,145
...做得太差了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...the slaying of your family.{\r}

192
00:30:21,363 --> 00:30:23,356
然而他费尽心思...
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Yet so much effort was spent...{\r}

193
00:30:23,574 --> 00:30:25,815
...对我隐瞒了这个事实
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...to conceal this matter from me.{\r}

194
00:30:27,953 --> 00:30:31,037
你说维克多为什么要隐瞒呢？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}What do you suppose Viktor had to hide?{\r}

195
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:35,290
而也许，是你吧，塞琳娜...
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Or perhaps it is you, Selene...{\r}

196
00:30:37,296 --> 00:30:40,961
...作为你肮脏家族的最后一员...
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...as the last of your wretched family...{\r}

197
00:30:41,717 --> 00:30:44,005
...是你有什么东西想瞒着我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...who has something to hide.{\r}

198
00:30:53,645 --> 00:30:55,056
快跑
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Go!{\r}

199
00:31:30,557 --> 00:31:31,755
进去
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get in.{\r}

200
00:32:39,710 --> 00:32:43,328
无论生死 你都要给我我想要的东西
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Dead or alive, you will give me what I want.{\r}

201
00:33:56,411 --> 00:33:58,071
你还好吧？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You okay?{\r}

202
00:34:01,917 --> 00:34:04,242
- 他是个混血儿，对吗？ - 是的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}- He's a hybrid, isn't he? - Yes.{\r}

203
00:34:05,420 --> 00:34:07,709
他想要这个 为什么呢？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}He wanted this. Why?{\r}

204
00:34:08,882 --> 00:34:10,507
我不知道
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't know.{\r}

205
00:34:10,717 --> 00:34:12,876
不过我们又有麻烦了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}But we have another problem.{\r}

206
00:34:18,100 --> 00:34:19,298
从这边开上去
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Turn off up here.{\r}

207
00:34:25,107 --> 00:34:27,099
妈的，好吧 趴下
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Shit. All right, get down.{\r}

208
00:34:28,235 --> 00:34:30,192
脚踩在油门上，趴好
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Keep your foot on the gas, but stay down.{\r}

209
00:34:46,003 --> 00:34:47,794
坚持住
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Hold on.{\r}

210
00:35:02,519 --> 00:35:04,144
别起身
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Stay down.{\r}

211
00:35:58,784 --> 00:36:00,243
来吧
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on.{\r}

212
00:36:17,845 --> 00:36:19,303
把手给我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Give me your hand.{\r}

213
00:36:19,513 --> 00:36:21,007
老天啊
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Jesus Christ.{\r}

214
00:36:22,683 --> 00:36:24,474
真的不需要
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}There's really no need.{\r}

215
00:36:24,685 --> 00:36:26,309
我去去就回
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll be right back.{\r}

216
00:36:43,036 --> 00:36:44,199
好吧，让我看看
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}All right, let me see.{\r}

217
00:36:49,168 --> 00:36:50,745
看到了？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}See?{\r}

218
00:36:50,961 --> 00:36:52,539
不需要
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}No need.{\r}

219
00:40:40,732 --> 00:40:41,930
长官，区域安全了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Area secure, sir.{\r}

220
00:42:09,696 --> 00:42:11,072
日落了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Sun's setting.{\r}

221
00:42:13,116 --> 00:42:14,492
怎么了？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}What's wrong?{\r}

222
00:42:21,416 --> 00:42:24,121
